structure.unit: PHYSICIANS, OSTEOPATHS, PODIATRISTS, AND RELATED MEDICAL PRACTITIONERS

law.history: Repealed 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 161, sec. 36, effective July 15, 2010. -- Amended 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 99, sec. 581, effective June 20, 2005. -- Amended 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 426, sec. 532, effective July 15, 1998. -- Amended 1992 Ky. Acts ch. 447, sec. 5, effective July 14, 1992. -- Created 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 19, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1986.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Hospitals to establish organ-procurement protocol -- Notification to federally certified organ-procurement organization of potential availability of organ and identity of potential donor -- Reporting of information on sale, purchase, or brokering of transplantable organs.
